g a\nchecklist for comparative studies of visual reasoning in humans and machines,\nwe hope to highlight how to overcome potential pitfalls in design or inference.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2020 16:05:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2020 08:37:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 13 Apr 2021 16:03:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-14"}
