ident with the GSS by chance is ~1%. Therefore, we claim that\nthese novae arose from the GSS progenitor, not M31 - the first confirmed novae\ndiscovered in a tidal steam.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2020 16:36:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-06"}
