ace insecure hash functions, even in large binaries (we tested\nones of size up to 1.5MB), while preserving existing functionality of the\noriginal binaries, and while incurring minimal execution-time overhead in the\nrewritten binaries. We also open source ALICE's code at\nhttps://github.com/SRI-CSL/ALICE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Apr 2020 02:27:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Apr 2020 02:56:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-23"}
