nce into false instanton vacuum. Observation of\nboson with rest mass $m_{X}$=17 MeV in the decay of high lying excited states\nof $^{8}$Be and $^{4}$He can possibly resolve one of the longest lasting open\nquestions in nuclear physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Apr 2020 05:23:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 May 2020 15:29:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 21 Jan 2021 11:26:59 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 10 Jun 2021 08:35:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-11"}
