} origin for these objects, i.e. perhaps the\nremnants of tidally stripped dwarfs. A further seven UCDs follow the GC\nrotation pattern, suggesting an \\textit{in-situ} origin and, possibly a GC-like\nnature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Apr 2020 08:31:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 24 May 2020 09:27:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-26"}
